1
00:00:03,170 --> 00:00:04,903
<i>When exposed to trauma,</i>

2
00:00:04,972 --> 00:00:07,256
<i>the body deploys its
own defense system.</i>

3
00:00:07,324 --> 00:00:08,485
Do you know why I resent you?

4
00:00:08,509 --> 00:00:10,642
I gave up everything for you.

5
00:00:14,214 --> 00:00:16,881
<i>From the first second the
brain receives the signal</i>

6
00:00:16,950 --> 00:00:19,518
<i>that a catastrophe
has happened...</i>

7
00:00:33,467 --> 00:00:35,345
You have a piece
of paper? For what?

8
00:00:35,369 --> 00:00:36,685
We need to make vows.

9
00:00:36,753 --> 00:00:39,521
I have Post-its.

10
00:00:39,590 --> 00:00:41,230
What do we want to
promise each other?

11
00:00:48,382 --> 00:00:51,742
<i>The blood rushes to the
organs that need help the most.</i>

12
00:00:53,153 --> 00:00:55,454
<i>Blood floods into the muscles,</i>

13
00:00:55,522 --> 00:00:57,989
<i>the lungs, the heart, the brain.</i>

14
00:01:11,488 --> 00:01:14,189
<i>The brain makes a decision
for the rest of the body.</i>

15
00:01:21,264 --> 00:01:23,831
<i>Either face the
danger or run away.</i>

16
00:01:32,293 --> 00:01:35,427
<i>It's a mechanism designed to
protect the body from harm...</i>

17
00:01:59,886 --> 00:02:03,489
<i>from knowing that what has
happened might be irreparable.</i>

18
00:02:03,557 --> 00:02:07,125
To love each other even
when we hate each other.

19
00:02:07,711 --> 00:02:08,743
No running.

20
00:02:13,116 --> 00:02:16,752
<i>We call it shock.</i>

21
00:02:26,129 --> 00:02:28,825
<i>The person who cares for
your kids is an important choice.</i>

22
00:02:28,849 --> 00:02:30,327
You want to make
sure it's the right fit.

23
00:02:30,351 --> 00:02:32,217
So we'll sit and talk.

24
00:02:32,285 --> 00:02:34,230
I'll find out about your
needs, you'll learn about me...

25
00:02:34,254 --> 00:02:36,454
Right. Just, right now,
I'm a little pressed for time.

26
00:02:36,490 --> 00:02:37,701
Oh, absolutely. You're busy.

27
00:02:37,725 --> 00:02:39,101
That's why we're here to help.

28
00:02:39,125 --> 00:02:41,226
Yeah, there's a trauma
coming in, and I...

29
