I know the drill.

31
00:02:46,166 --> 00:02:47,727
How about if I wait in the
lobby until you have some time?

32
00:02:47,751 --> 00:02:49,911
That's great. I'll
find you. Okay.

33
00:02:50,954 --> 00:02:52,220
Who was that?

34
