118
00:05:51,518 --> 00:05:53,263
When do I get to speak
to her previous doctors?

119
00:05:53,287 --> 00:05:55,231
Um, as soon as I
talk to Dr. Herman.

120
00:05:55,255 --> 00:05:57,088
