130
00:06:17,477 --> 00:06:18,910
She'll be happy.

131
00:06:18,978 --> 00:06:20,679
Ultimately, she
will be thrilled.

132
00:06:22,683 --> 00:06:23,948
You want me to tell her?

133
00:06:24,017 --> 00:06:25,328
No. I have to do
it. I have to do it.

134
00:06:25,352 --> 00:06:27,352
I just need to figure
out how and when.

135
00:06:27,421 --> 00:06:29,120
How and when.

136
00:06:32,926 --> 00:06:34,709
That's my tumor.

137
00:06:34,777 --> 00:06:37,195
That's my tumor!

138
00:06:37,264 --> 00:06:39,748
Where did you get it
and why do you have it?

139
00:06:47,140 --> 00:06:48,873
You showed my tumor

140
00:06:48,942 --> 00:06:50,052
to other doctors

141
00:06:50,076 --> 00:06:51,196
without my consent?

142
00:06:51,278 --> 00:06:52,878
I needed to understand...

143
00:06:52,946 --> 00:06:54,490
You have no right.
You stole them.

144
00:06:54,514 --> 00:06:55,764
I had to.

145
00:06:55,832 --> 00:06:57,594
Do you know how many
laws you're breaking right now?

146
00:06:57,618 --> 00:06:59,133
