148
00:07:00,737 --> 00:07:02,281
I don't know who you've
been seeing for this.

149
00:07:02,305 --> 00:07:03,671
I'm sure they're great.

150
00:07:03,740 --> 00:07:05,418
I'm sure they are
the best in their field.

151
00:07:05,442 --> 00:07:09,093
But I can only tell you
they lack imagination.

152
00:07:09,162 --> 00:07:10,402
They lack scope.

153
00:07:11,515 --> 00:07:13,748
Your tumor is smart.

154
00:07:13,817 --> 00:07:15,600
It's brilliant.

155
00:07:15,669 --> 00:07:18,069
But so am I. I can beat it.

156
00:07:18,639 --> 00:07:19,904
I will beat it.

157
00:07:26,379 --> 00:07:27,545
I have a surgery.

158
00:07:37,140 --> 00:07:38,873
Chief, uh, just
wanted to let you know

159
00:07:38,942 --> 00:07:40,520
