gonna make it in today.

160
00:07:40,544 --> 00:07:41,726
We had some news...

161
00:07:41,795 --> 00:07:42,955
April's here.

162
00:07:44,064 --> 00:07:45,346
Wait. What?

163
00:07:45,415 --> 00:07:46,692
Yeah. She's been
here all morning.

164
00:07:46,716 --> 00:07:48,060
She's just on her
way up to surgery.

165
00:07:48,084 --> 00:07:49,417
Everything okay?

166
00:07:49,486 --> 00:07:51,353
Uh, yeah, yeah. Thank you.

167
00:07:53,089 --> 00:07:54,588
You know what? No.

168
00:07:54,657 --> 00:07:56,502
Actually, I need you to pull
her out of surgery right now.

169
00:07:56,526 --> 00:07:58,822
Avery, I can't... No, look.
She shouldn't operate.

170
00:07:58,846 --> 00:08:00,745
She shouldn't even
be at work today at all,

171
00:08:00,814 --> 00:08:02,547
so she should definitely
not be operating.

172
00:08:02,616 --> 00:08:04,216
