me when I say that.

173
00:08:05,768 --> 00:08:06,845
Kelly, more lap pads?

174
00:08:06,869 --> 00:08:08,114
I think I see the
source of the cut.

175
00:08:08,138 --> 00:08:09,258
I got it.

176
