212
00:09:34,641 --> 00:09:38,226
Got some bruises and
contusions, nothing surgical.

213
00:09:38,295 --> 00:09:39,556
You guys had a
pretty rough ride, huh?

214
00:09:39,580 --> 00:09:40,780
It was awesome.

215
00:09:40,814 --> 00:09:42,608
