234
00:10:19,969 --> 00:10:21,769
Looks like it.

235
00:10:21,837 --> 00:10:23,633
What happened
with you and Kepner?

236
00:10:23,657 --> 00:10:24,823
Nothing.

237
00:10:24,891 --> 00:10:25,935
