00:38:04,249 --> 00:38:05,798
Why would that happen?

786
00:38:05,867 --> 00:38:09,135
Why would God give her kids,
give her a family, and let that...

787
00:38:10,405 --> 00:38:12,238
Why would God let that happen?

788
00:38:12,324 --> 00:38:14,607
I don't understand it!

789
00:38:14,676 --> 00:38:17,794
You can do everything
right, and it doesn't even...

790
00:38:20,866 --> 00:38:22,465
Why?

791
00:38:25,720 --> 00:38:26,960
I don't know.

792
00:38:29,557 --> 00:38:31,490
I don't know.

793
00:38:33,327 --> 00:38:35,010
I... I just...

794
