00:40:55,303 --> 00:40:56,369
<i>Okay.</i>

841
00:40:58,005 --> 00:40:59,639
Call me when you land.

842
00:40:59,708 --> 00:41:01,140
<i>And, Derek?</i>

843
00:41:01,209 --> 00:41:02,575
Yes?

844
00:41:02,644 --> 00:41:04,544
<i>I'm going to miss you.</i>

845
00:41:06,248 --> 00:41:07,547
This can work.

846
00:41:07,616 --> 00:41:08,881
We will make this work.

847
00:41:08,950 --> 00:41:10,566
We will.

848
00:41:10,635 --> 00:41:12,451
Are you still there?

849
00:41:12,520 --> 00:41:13,552
Meredith?

850
00:41:16,741 --> 00:41:18,502
Meredith? Meredith,
I'm losing you.

851
00:41:18,526 --> 00:41:19,759
Derek?

852
00:41:29,353 --> 00:41:33,389
This is forever.

853
00:41:38,213 --> 00:41:39,311
Sign.

854
00:41:51,375 --> 00:41:53,025
Now what?

855
00:41:53,094 --> 00:41:54,860
Now I kiss the bride.

856
00:42:07,959 --> 00:42:10,209
<i>The shock response
had protected us,</i>

